OL,3,CHome Office 'cut corners' and 'wasted'
OL,4,C#15m on asbestos-riddled migrant camp
OL,6,FNortheye was "deemed unfit for its
OL,7,Fintended purpose due to
OL,8,Fcontamination", after the purchase of
OL,9,Fabout #15.4 million had gone through,
OL,10,Fthe report reveals.
OL,12,FThe NAO also found the government paid
OL,13,Fmore than double the price the site
OL,14,Fhad been bought for in 2022 - around
OL,15,F#6.3 million.
OL,17,FCampaigners say the revelations prove
OL,18,Fthat the policy of creating "camps" in
OL,19,Fthe asylum system should be abandoned.
