OL,3,CHome Office 'cut corners' and 'wasted'
OL,4,C#15m on asbestos-riddled migrant camp
OL,6,FLou Calvey, director of charity Asylum
OL,7,FMatters, accused the previous
OL,8,Fgovernment of "ignoring warnings so it
OL,9,Fcould indulge in waste and
OL,10,Fcarelessness, putting cruel ideology
OL,11,Fabove everything else ` including
OL,12,Fvalue for the taxpayer".
OL,14,F"If more proof were needed of how ill-
OL,15,Fthought-out the policy of camps in our
OL,16,Fasylum system is, this is it," she
OL,17,Fsaid.
