OL,6,F"Our new Government must take the
OL,7,Flesson from this fiasco, and
OL,8,Fimmediately abandon plans to place
OL,9,Fpeople seeking safety in any large-
OL,10,Fscale site like this."
OL,12,FThe chairman of a Commons committee
OL,13,Fwhich scrutinises government spending
OL,14,Fcriticised the Home Office for
OL,15,F"overpaying" for a site which was "not
OL,16,Ffit for purpose" and said MPs would
OL,17,Fmake sure taxpayers' cash was not
OL,18,F"wasted in future acquisitions".
