OL,4,C#15m on asbestos-riddled migrant camp
OL,6,FThe sale came after then-prime
OL,7,Fminister Rishi Sunak vowed on December
OL,8,F13 2022 to stop housing asylum seekers
OL,9,Fin hotels - and find accommodation in
OL,10,Fdisused holiday parks, former student
OL,11,Fhalls and surplus military sites.
OL,13,FThe statement in Parliament "generated
OL,14,Fsignificant pressure within the Home
OL,15,FOffice to identify and secure sites
OL,16,Ffor asylum accommodation at pace", the
OL,17,Freport said.
