OL,6,FIn February 2023 planning checks
OL,7,Frevealed "high risk" contamination
OL,8,Facross the site and a further review
OL,9,Fconcluded the "primary contamination
OL,10,Frisk was from asbestos-containing
OL,11,Fmaterials in existing buildings and
OL,12,Fcontaminated ground".
OL,14,FA "due diligence report" also
OL,15,Findicated repairs to buildings could
OL,16,Fcost "in excess of #20 million" but
OL,17,Fthis was not mentioned in the Home
OL,18,FOffice's internal advice, the NAO said.
