OL,6,FRobert Jenrick, former immigration
OL,7,Fminister, announced on March 29 2023
OL,8,Fthat his government would develop the
OL,9,FNortheye site to house 1,200 migrants.
OL,10,FThe purchase was then completed in
OL,11,FSeptember 2023.
