OL,6,FThe NAO's report concludes: "The Home
OL,7,FOffice's attempt to acquire the
OL,8,FNortheye site within just a few
OL,9,Fmonths... led it to cut corners and
OL,10,Fmake a series of poor decisions.
OL,12,F"This resulted in it purchasing a site
OL,13,Fthat was unsuitable for that original
OL,14,Fpurpose and it paying more for it than
OL,15,Fit needed to."
