OL,6,FIn July this year, the Home Office
OL,7,Fsaid no decision had been made on the
OL,8,Fuse of the site and it would "consider
OL,9,Fits strategy and broader requirements
OL,10,Fbefore taking a view on the future use
OL,11,Fof it".
OL,13,FThe Home Office noted the report was
OL,14,Fabout the actions of a previous
OL,15,Fgovernment, and said it remained
OL,16,Fcommitted to ending the use of hotels
OL,17,Fto house those going through the
OL,18,Fasylum system.
